{"tid":731050,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[FakeNews]MK暉話有不少\"中國球迷\"為日本隊打氣, 睇原片啲\"中國球迷\"講日文既屌你","createTime":"2018-07-06T01:56:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-06T03:09:54.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e596c391146868ecd2090eb78c8f2f43a45522ea","tid":731050,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T01:56:00.000Z","msg":"堅離地城：沈旭暉國際生活台 Simon's Glocal World<br />\nJuly 3 at 12:30 PM &middot; <br />\n[#WorldCup🇯🇵🇨🇳] 其實也有不少中國球迷為日本隊打氣，不要盡信官媒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/36383542_1995533020480838_3598213666605891584_n.jpg?_nc_cat=0&amp;oh=281d35d525992ca4c99dcbf868db9c34&amp;oe=5BD7358D\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F36383542_1995533020480838_3598213666605891584_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D0%26oh%3D281d35d525992ca4c99dcbf868db9c34%26oe%3D5BD7358D&h=766e5440&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(Source: Cameron Wilson Twitter)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/shensimon/?hc_ref=ARQolCR8DGU-z8fMgsvmLEX-xYezayM6YrPQn5b0WaG1L6AXexKfibRxMKcGcbFXFZw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fshensimon%2F%3Fhc_ref%3DARQolCR8DGU-z8fMgsvmLEX-xYezayM6YrPQn5b0WaG1L6AXexKfibRxMKcGcbFXFZw&d=OUlNw5GLxpc95nyVxkAcHG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=05f2d7ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/shensimon/?hc_ref=ARQolCR8DGU-z8fMgsvmLEX-xYezayM6YrPQn5b0WaG1L6AXexKfibRxMKcGcbFXFZw</a><br />\n<br />\n原本嗰twitter有埋片, 嗰幾條友講日文<br />\nI love football because it leads us to challenge established ways of thinking. <strong>Here are Chinese people wearing Japan shirts <span style=\"color: red;\">leading the chants of &quot;Nippon!&quot;</span> in Shanghai last night. </strong>Chinese Football is deeper and more nuanced than most realise. Just like China itself.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/CameronWEF/status/1012527878511124480\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCameronWEF%2Fstatus%2F1012527878511124480&d=OUlNw5GLxpc95nyVxkAcHG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=014bf511\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCameronWEF%2Fstatus%2F1012527878511124480&h=59651c59\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/CameronWEF/status/1012527878511124480</a><br />\n<br />\n啲相既原post:<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/CameronWEF/status/1012669934906667010\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCameronWEF%2Fstatus%2F1012669934906667010&d=OUlNw5GLxpc95nyVxkAcHG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=9fba93e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCameronWEF%2Fstatus%2F1012669934906667010&h=bb9e2da6\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/CameronWEF/status/1012669934906667010</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網上評論:<br />\n有這樣一名外國記者，名字叫作Cameron Wilson,中文名字是韋侃崙，他的認證是中國足球記者和顧問。他在推特上發表了一些照片、視頻和相應的文字解說，他這樣寫道：&ldquo;一些中國球迷在上海某酒吧身著日本球衣，並同日本球迷一起高喊日本隊，這些中國人在日本同波蘭的比賽中與日本球迷一同支持日本隊&rdquo;，從照片中確實可以看到一群身穿日本隊球衣的人，而且還有一面集合了中日兩國國旗的旗幟，上寫中日友好，而視頻中的助威聲音就是日本（抱歉視頻我沒有貼上），不過自始至終都是用日語喊的。<br />\n<br />\n所以通過以上分析，可以推斷出上述可能只是部分事實：雖然有中國元素在其中，但是可能上述人員都是在華的日本人而已，在中國工作或者求學，身在中國才同時出現了中國國旗，然後給人造成了有當地中國人參與的假象。<br />\n<br />\n當然了，誰支持誰都是他們的自由，我也管不著，通過足球促進中日兩國人民友好是很歡迎的，反正是足球，又不是其他的。不過我不支持日本隊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.xuehua.us/2018/06/30/%E6%9B%9D%E8%BA%AB%E7%A9%BF%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E9%98%9F%E7%90%83%E8%A1%A3%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E7%90%83%E8%BF%B7%E5%9C%A8%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E6%9F%90%E9%85%92%E5%90%A7%E9%AB%98%E5%96%8A%E6%97%A5/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.xuehua.us%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F%25E6%259B%259D%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E7%25A9%25BF%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E9%2598%259F%25E7%2590%2583%25E8%25A1%25A3%25E7%259A%2584%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259B%25BD%25E7%2590%2583%25E8%25BF%25B7%25E5%259C%25A8%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E6%259F%2590%25E9%2585%2592%25E5%2590%25A7%25E9%25AB%2598%25E5%2596%258A%25E6%2597%25A5%2F&d=OUlNw5GLxpc95nyVxkAcHG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=92acbc1b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.xuehua.us/2018/06/30/%E6%9B%9D%E8%BA%AB%E7%A9%BF%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E9%98%9F%E7%90%83%E8%A1%A3%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E7%90%83%E8%BF%B7%E5%9C%A8%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E6%9F%90%E9%85%92%E5%90%A7%E9%AB%98%E5%96%8A%E6%97%A5/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實為日本隊打氣既都係日本人，不要盡信官媒沈旭暉"},{"pid":"a4ca2dbb55c3d10607a0d5720cbfa420f61ce65b","tid":731050,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T01:57:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dccd40b39e6c97b31dc45c4df5e209cdff1025a","tid":731050,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T03:09:54.000Z","msg":"又中<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}